  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your prowess in Aldori swordplay grants you bravado.</em><br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You gain a +2 morale bonus on Intimidate checks to demoralize opponents, and the DC of any attempt to demoralize you increases by 2. When you're participating in a duel, these bonuses increase to +4.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>During any combat that is not a duel, you can spend 1 stamina point at the start of your turn to treat the combat as a duel until the start of your next turn for the purpose of gaining the benefits of the Aldori Dueling Discipline feat.",
